@AWE.ApiGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5192

GET {{AWE.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

# ================= EXECUTION MANAGEMENT =================

### Get Paged List of Executions
GET {{AWE.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/executions?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get specific Execution Details (with Pointers)
GET {{AWE.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/executions/YOUR_EXECUTION_ID_HERE
Accept: application/json

### Get Logs for an Execution
GET {{AWE.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/executions/YOUR_EXECUTION_ID_HERE/logs
Accept: application/json

### Suspend an Execution
POST {{AWE.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/executions/YOUR_EXECUTION_ID_HERE/suspend
Content-Type: application/json

### Resume an Execution
POST {{AWE.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/executions/YOUR_EXECUTION_ID_HERE/resume
Content-Type: application/json

### Retry an Execution (Re-submit failed execution using identical inputs)
POST {{AWE.ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/executions/YOUR_EXECUTION_ID_HERE/retry
Content-Type: application/json

###
